<br>
The problem is I go to school, work, the gf, etc. and I am not in the house all the time, and they have downloaded a trojan horse program, and lots of other programs that have affected the operation of my comp.  I even had to delete and reinstall EQ last week.  And the idea of one of them downloading 'pictures' at my computer and what they 'do' with those pictures bothers me.<br>
<br>
I run Windows xp, and I am mostly computer ignorant.  (Well, mostly ignorant in general, but that is a different story =P.)  Is there a way to set up the computer so when it is turned on they would have to enter a password?  If so please let me know.  And thanks in advance.<br>
<br>
