<br>
<br>
Go into the control panel, into Users and Passwords, select your usename and click the Set Password button.<br>
<br>
<br>
The passowrd is most likely blank right now.  Set it to something you will remember and your roommates won't guess.<br>
<br>
Now click on shut down, take the log off option.<br>
<br>
Hit ctrl+alt+delete and enter your user name and password.<br>
<br>
<br>
Now any time you leave your computer, simply hit ctrl+alt+delete again and select the Lock Worstation option.  When you come back, hit ctrl+alt+delete again and enter your password.  <br>
<br>
Unless your roommates get your password they won't be able to unlock the machine. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=liffthemage>Liff the Mage</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 169<br> <font color=#333333>(2/19/03 8:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8834.topic&index=6>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Password</span><hr size=1> Thanks Much, I will do these tonight when I get home.  You all rule  =). <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=celanxev>CelanXev</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Conjurer</span><br>  Posts: 265<br> <font color=#333333>(2/19/03 8:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8834.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re:</span><hr size=1> I'd hate to be in a room with people that go on my computer. <br>
